    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从一颗鱼卵开始的奇迹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你心仪的鱼卵，轻轻放入水族箱中，静待新的水中伙伴破壳而出。悉心照料这些小生命，满足它们的各种需求，看着它们从幼鱼成长为美丽的成体。每一次孵化都是一个全新的开始，而这仅仅是探索数千种鱼类的第一步！通过精心调节水温、盐分和光照等环境条件，为不同鱼种创造最适宜的生存环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/e170ecad80be2175838fc8af6f190c21.poster.avif?t=1758009961\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/e170ecad80be2175838fc8af6f190c21.webm?t=1758009961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/e170ecad80be2175838fc8af6f190c21.mp4?t=1758009961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限融合的基因密码</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将心爱的鱼类放入特殊的繁殖池中，开启无限融合的神奇旅程！尝试各种组合搭配，发现前所未见的全新物种。鱼儿们越快乐，繁殖成功率就越高。通过满足鱼类需求获得快乐值，再用这些快乐值解锁更多繁殖可能。每一次融合都可能诞生独一无二的鱼种，让你的水族箱成为真正的生物多样性宝库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/a7a8cdd0d72a28a5e65cde7e7a8778d5.poster.avif?t=1758009961\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/a7a8cdd0d72a28a5e65cde7e7a8778d5.webm?t=1758009961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/a7a8cdd0d72a28a5e65cde7e7a8778d5.mp4?t=1758009961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造专属水下王国</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用丰富多样的装饰品、水草、增益道具和背景，将水族箱装扮成独一无二的水下世界。每一个装饰都不仅仅是美观，更能影响鱼儿们的心情和繁殖效果。即使你离开游戏，水族箱也会继续繁荣发展。随时回来查看鱼类图鉴，收集和使用快乐值，规划水族箱的未来发展，让这场水下冒险永不停歇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/0755874b12fd8056642d90456d20427f.poster.avif?t=1758009961\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/0755874b12fd8056642d90456d20427f.webm?t=1758009961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338820/extras/0755874b12fd8056642d90456d20427f.mp4?t=1758009961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
